snippet.title: [Murasaki7] Anime Puzzle - RPG Teaser
snippet.description:
Murasaki7 - Anime, Puzzle - RPG, Cards
Platform: Android & iOS
Release Date: TBA

Murasaki7 is an exciting new spin on the Anime, Puzzle-RPG genre featuring a unique story with over 300 levels, elements of Unit Collection, PVP rankings, and an awesome rewards system!
